<div class="bg-gray-400 text-black py-12">
  <div class="container max-w-2xl text-center">
    <p>
      Want to receive approximately one email every month with new articles,
      tools, and references I've discovered? Sign up below.
    </p>
    <form
      action="https://buttondown.email/api/emails/embed-subscribe/seancdavis29"
      method="post"
      target="popupwindow"
      onsubmit="window.open('https://buttondown.email/seancdavis29', 'popupwindow')"
      class="embeddable-buttondown-form mb-4"
    >
      <input type="hidden" value="1" name="embed"></input>

      <span class="sm:flex justify-center">
        <input
          type="email"
          name="email"
          id="bd-email"
          placeholder="Enter your email"
          aria-label="Email Address"
          required
          class="
            bg-transparent
            border-black
            border-2
            mb-2
            mr-2
            placeholder-gray-700
            py-1
            px-2
            text-black
            w-64
            sm:mb-0
          "
        >
        <input
          type="submit"
          value="Subscribe"
          class="
            bg-transparent
            border-2
            border-black
            cursor-pointer
            duration-300
            font-sans
            inline-block
            px-6
            py-1
            relative
            text-sm
            text-black
            transition-all
            uppercase
            hover:bg-black
            hover:text-white"
          ></input>
      </span>
    </form>

    <p class="text-sm">
      <a href="/blog/introducing-the-spinneret">More info here.</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="bg-black text-white py-12">
  <div class="container max-w-4xl md:flex justify-between text-center md:text-left">
    <div class="md:max-w-xs mb-8">
      <a href="/" class="inline-block w-12 mb-4">
        {% svg "seancdavis-logo-white" %}
        <span class="visible-hidden">Home</span>
      </a>
      <div class="text-sm max-w-sm mx-auto md:mx-0 links-inherit-color links-underline">
        {% markdown %}
This site was created and is maintained by [Sean C Davis](https://twitter.com/seancdavis29). It was designed by [Matt Willett](https://mattwillettdesign.com/).

The stack is [Eleventy](https://www.11ty.dev/), [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com/), and loads of other open-source software. The code is built, deployed, and hosted with help from [GitHub](https://github.com/) and [Netlify](https://www.netlify.com/).

And here's [a super important legal document](/license) Sean made up.
        {% endmarkdown %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:flex">
      {% for menu in footer_menus %}
        <div class="md:ml-8">
          <span class="block mb-2 font-sans uppercase font-bold text-xs opacity-50">
            {{ menu.heading }}
          </span>
          <ul>
            {% for link in menu.links %}
              <li class="block">
                <a href="{{ link.url }}" class="text-white hover:opacity-75 transition-all duration-300">
                  {{ link.label }}
                </a>
              </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
